-- MOVES-Old Mutual Global hires Ian Ormiston from Ignis Asset Management 
-- By Anet Josline Pinto in Bangalore
-- Tue Oct 07, 2014 06:28AM EDT
-- None



Oct 7 (Reuters) - Old Mutual Global Investors Ltd, the asset management division of Old Mutual Wealth, appointed Ian Ormiston as manager in its European smaller companies fund.

Ormiston, who has been managing European equities for over 20 years, will lead the development and launch of a new European smaller companies fund, the company said. He joins from Ignis Asset Management Ltd, where he worked as a European equities portfolio manager for 7 years.